from models.registry.model_types import ModelType
from models.registry.model_registry import ModelRegistry
from models.architectures.transformers.resolution_specific.subhourly_transformer import SubhourlyTransformer
from models.architectures.transformers.resolution_specific.hourly_transformer import HourlyTransformer
from models.architectures.transformers.resolution_specific.daily_transformer import DailyTransformer
from models.architectures.transformers.resolution_specific.monthly_transformer import MonthlyTransformer

def register_models():
    """Register all model types with the registry."""
    ModelRegistry.register(ModelType.SUBHOURLY_TRANSFORMER, SubhourlyTransformer)
    ModelRegistry.register(ModelType.HOURLY_TRANSFORMER, HourlyTransformer)
    ModelRegistry.register(ModelType.DAILY_TRANSFORMER, DailyTransformer)
    ModelRegistry.register(ModelType.MONTHLY_TRANSFORMER, MonthlyTransformer)
